com.snamp

Class Range<L extends java.lang.Comparable<L>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snamp.Range<L>
  • Type Parameters:
    L - Type of the range elements.

    public class Range<L extends java.lang.Comparable<L>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents range of values.

    Example:

    final Range<Integer> r = new Range<>(1, 10);
     final boolean b = r.contains(5, InclusionTestType.FULL_INCLUSIVE);

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Roman Sakno
